Global Organic Mattress Market Insights
Organic Mattress Market size was valued at USD 4.95 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 10.6 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 10.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Organic Mattress Market Overview
The global organic mattress market has experienced significant growth, with sales reaching approximately 1.9 million units in 2021. Projections indicate a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of around 8.2%, anticipating a market valuation of $13.87 billion by 2032. This growth is driven by increasing consumer demand for eco-friendly and health-conscious bedding options.

